Smile like this.

270
00:18:26,270 --> 00:18:27,710
A hearty smile?

271
00:18:27,710 --> 00:18:29,850
What? You know this word?

272
00:18:29,850 --> 00:18:32,640
I'm starting to wonder.

273
00:18:32,640 --> 00:18:36,621
If your Thai is this good, why did you hire me as your interpreter?

274
00:18:36,621 --> 00:18:38,510
I don't want an interpreter.

275
00:18:38,510 --> 00:18:40,086
I want a manager.

276
00:18:40,086 --> 00:18:41,140
What?

277
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:43,901
She asked me to be your interpreter.

278
00:18:43,901 --> 00:18:46,300
She's paying me 5,000 THB a day. That's why I came.

279
00:18:46,300 --> 00:18:47,341
Is that so?

280
00:18:47,341 --> 00:18:48,541
Yeah.

281
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:56,430
Oh, that's why.

282
00:18:56,430 --> 00:19:00,615
That's why I had to accompany you to many places and was in charge of many things.

283
00:19:00,615 --> 00:19:02,916
I was tricked?

284
00:19:02,916 --> 00:19:04,343
Gosh!

285
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:09,255
But don't worry.

286
00:19:09,255 --> 00:19:11,280
I won't stay and annoy you for long.

287
00:19:11,280 --> 00:19:14,380
After this job is done, I'll leave.

288
00:19:14,380 --> 00:19:15,940
What are you going to do?

289
00:19:15,940 --> 00:19:18,731
I'll do my job.

290
00:19:19,518 --> 00:19:21,566
I'm a teacher.

291
00:19:21,566 --> 00:19:23,080
Teaching English?

292
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:25,526
Yeah. How did you know?

293
00:19:25,526 --> 00:19:27,458
You have a good accent. It's easy to guess.

294
00:19:27,458 --> 00:19:29,316
Not really.

295
00:19:29,316 --> 00:19:31,260
I only teach kindergarten students.

296
00:19:31,260 --> 00:19:34,105
I teach them simple phonetics. Sometimes, I teach them singing

297
00:19:34,105 --> 00:19:36,880
and just some basic vocabulary.

298
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:39,040
Does that mean you love kids?

299
00:19:43,180 --> 00:19:46,439
Not really.

300
00:19:46,439 --> 00:19:48,933
It's not that I love kids.

301
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:55,007
But it's more because I like the moment when parents come to pick their kids up.

302
00:19:55,007 --> 00:19:56,407
Why?

303
00:19:58,240 --> 00:20:02,961
When I see them hug, I feel so good.

304
00:20:03,900 --> 00:20:11,284
When the kids see their parents come to pick them up,

305
00:20:11,284 --> 00:20:14,818
they run all the way, jump towards them and hug them.

306
00:20:14,818 --> 00:20:17,980
It looks so genuine. I can feel it.

307
00:20:17,980 --> 00:20:21,391
It's not pretentious.

308
00:20:21,391 --> 00:20:26,618
It gives me such positive energy.

309
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:44,860
Well, to be honest,

310
00:20:46,920 --> 00:20:48,620
I think...

311
00:20:52,067 --> 00:20:56,186
I'm kind of envious of those kids.

312
00:21:29,321 --> 00:21:33,166
I think I'm sleepy now.

313
00:21:33,166 --> 00:21:37,181
I yawned too much that my eyes got teary.

314
00:21:43,420 --> 00:21:47,390
I'll go to bed.

315
00:21:47,390 --> 00:21:48,890
Goodnight.

316
00:22:07,940 --> 00:22:09,878
Here you are.

317
00:22:11,815 --> 00:22:15,467
Warm milk for a good sleep.

318
00:22:15,940 --> 00:22:18,040
Thank you.

319
00:22:18,040 --> 00:22:19,410
I'm going in.

320
00:22:52,010 --> 00:22:54,470
