388
00:28:20,246 --> 00:28:22,332
All right?

389
00:28:22,332 --> 00:28:24,702
Don't promise.

390
00:28:29,889 --> 00:28:31,360
By the way,

391
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:35,452
