511
00:35:39,787 --> 00:35:41,000
What's his name?

512
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:42,560
Please just call me Dino.

513
00:35:42,560 --> 00:35:44,650
All right.

514
00:35:44,650 --> 00:35:46,840
Thanks a lot, Dino.

